    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle offers a practical entry point for anyone seeking low-cost transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows the wear you\u2019d expect from an older used vehicle, but it still presents a strong value for buyers who prioritize price and potential. A sensible choice for someone looking for dependable basic utility without a major upfront investment.",
