    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car being sold as-is, and a great fit for someone who wants affordable wheels without spending a fortune. It\u2019s not a showroom piece, but it\u2019s a solid opportunity for a handy buyer, commuter on a budget, or anyone looking for a simple runabout with some life left in it. Priced fairly and represented straight \u2014 if you\u2019re after cheap transportation with potential, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget driver with a strong-running engine, responsive automatic transmission, and good oil pressure. The drivetrain feels willing, steering is direct, and it has the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes it a great candidate for someone who wants an affordable entry point and room to improve it over time. Not a show car, but it presents as a complete, usable vehicle with plenty of upside for a hands-on owner. Priced to move and hard to beat for someone looking for inexpensive transportation or a straightforward fixer-upper.",
      "price": 5950.0,
