    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of road-worn character you can\u2019t fake\u2014a seasoned companion with stories in every panel and plenty of life left for the right next chapter. It\u2019s an ideal find for someone who sees potential instead of perfection: a budget-friendly ride, a hands-on project, or a dependable around-town cruiser with unmistakable personality. If you\u2019ve been looking for something affordable, memorable, and full of possibility, this one is ready to earn its next adventure.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Honest, affordable transportation with solid value for the right buyer. This vehicle is being offered as a budget-friendly option with visible age and wear consistent with its condition, making it a smart choice for someone seeking inexpensive wheels, a project, or a practical second car. Priced to reflect condition while still delivering real utility, it represents a straightforward opportunity from a seller who believes in clear, transparent listings.",
