      "description": "Looking for a cheap runabout or a solid project to tinker with? This one isn\u2019t pretty, but it\u2019s an affordable way into a car with plenty of potential for the right buyer. Ideal for someone handy, after spare parts, or needing a budget option that doesn\u2019t break the bank. Priced to sell and ready to go to its next home.",
